thread.title: Asclepias

author: Asclepias
title: Asclepias
text: I was VERY impressed with LEDSupply! I only needed to make a ridiculously small purchase, but I still got free shipping and it came fast. They package things very carefully (bubble wrap inside a padded envelope) and it was exactly what I needed. My LED is already soldered in place and it works great! This will be the first store I'll check when I need to make bigger purchases for bigger projects.
